---
---

<section class="section" id="roadmap">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">Roadmap</span>
    <h2 class="roadmap-title">More on the way</h2>
    <p class="roadmap-lead">
      Smarter warning handling is just the first step. smix will keep growing
      with more capabilities layered on top of Mix.
    </p>

    <div class="roadmap-grid">
      <div class="r-card r-done">
        <span class="tag tag-done">Available</span>
        <h3>Warning management</h3>
        <p>Ignore all, branch-only, and mute-with-a-comment.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="r-card r-next">
        <span class="tag tag-next">Coming soon</span>
        <h3>TBD</h3>
        <p>The next capability is in design. Stay tuned.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .roadmap-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .roadmap-lead {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .roadmap-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  .r-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 22px;
    background: var(--bg-elev);
  }
  .r-next {
    border-style: dashed;
    background: transparent;
  }
  .r-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin: 12px 0 8px;
  }
  .r-card p {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 3px 9px;
    border-radius: 999px;
  }
  .tag-done {
    color: var(--ok);
    background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.12);
  }
  .tag-next {
    color: var(--fg-faint);
    background: var(--bg-elev);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .roadmap-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
